<CHAPTER ID="chapter.mim">
  <TITLE/Mozart Instant Messenger/
    <AUTHOR.EXTERN TO="author.db" KEY="Nils.Franzen">
    <AUTHOR.EXTERN TO="author.db" KEY="Simon.Lindblom">

  <P><LIST CLASS=linkmenu>
      <ITEM/<REF.EXTERN
      TO="applets/MIM.oza"/Start Client//
      <ITEM/<REF.EXTERN
      TO="http://www.sics.se/mozart/mim/"/More Information//
      <ITEM><REF.EXTERN TO="ozdoc:install" KEY="applets"/How to enable Applets/
    </LIST></P>
  <SECTION CLASS=unnumbered>
    <TITLE/Starting a Client/
    <P>First a window pops up and prompts you for a login name and a
    password. If this is your first session, click on the "New User"
    button and fill-in the fields. Use <KEY/TAB/ to move between the
    fields and press <KEY/RET/ when done. More information about
    <EM>Mozart Instant messenger</EM> is found <REF.EXTERN
    TO="http://www.sics.se/mozart/mim/">here</REF.EXTERN>.
</SECTION>
</CHAPTER>

